contact_name: European Commission JRC Institute for Energy and Transport

resources.description: Datasets from PhD work on P91 small punch creep & fracture tests

description: Data produced during work to evaluate the creep and fracture properties of P91 steel by small punch testing.  The tests were performed on material extracted from the same pipe used in the INTEGRITY FP5 Growth Project (GRD 1/10886. 2005.), the data for which are also hosted at the JRC Petten ODIN portal.
title: Test data for small punch fracture on material P91 haz_fg at -168 Celsius and a displacement rate of 0.0055 mm/s
name: jrcpett-odin-test-material-p91-410028
contact_address: EC - JRC Petten, Institute for Energy and Transport, P.O.Box 2, NL-1755 ZG, Petten, Noord Holland, The Netherlands
